  "_note": "Per-entry _verification_status records sourcing. cross_references.* populated at X.D.1 back-fill (currently all null). The 13-49 00 00 umbrella entry is excluded from entries[] as the parent_category header. The secondary mirror exposes six sub-trees under 13-49: Anechoic Chamber (13-49 11), Hazard Containment (13-49 13), Clean Room (13-49 15, 10 leaf entries), Temperature and Pressure Chamber (13-49 17), Data Center (13-49 19, 5 entries), Controlled Space Support (13-49 21), and Miscellaneous Environmentally Controlled Spaces (13-49 23, 2 leaf entries). All 25 entries below the umbrella are mirror_sourced verbatim. Entry count (25) exceeds the master-index target (22) because the mirror coverage of 13-49 is dense across all sub-trees — consistent with the pattern established in artistic_spaces (32 > 16). Clean room ISO classifications reference ISO 14644-1 particle-count classes as stated verbatim in the mirror; the ISO standard number is cited from the mirror definition, not from direct access to the paid ISO document. Data Center Tier designations follow the Uptime Institute Tier Standard verbatim as stated in the mirror. All environmentally controlled spaces are enclosed interior spaces; ifc_space_type=INTERNAL for all entries per IfcSpaceTypeEnum (ISO 16739). Future Sprint Y back-fill from the canonical OCCS PDF (CSI license) will raise _verification_status from mirror_sourced to occs_verified.",
